ena Bremerhaven]], [[Bremerhaven]]\n|date1=1 March\n|score1=1\u20134\n|recap1=www.telekomeishockey.de/event/erc-ingolstadt-pinguins-bremerhaven/784\n|won1=2\n|1-1-1=[[David Elsner]] \u2013 09:10\n|1-1-2=19:30 \u2013 [[Jeremy Welsh]]\n|1-2-2=29:24 \u2013 [[Bronson Maschmeyer]]<br>31:57 \u2013 Welsh\n|1-3-2=58:55 \u2013 [[Jack Combs (ice hockey)|Jack Combs]] (ENG)\n|goalie1-1=[[Timo Pielmeier]] (35 saves / 38 shots)\n|goalie1-2=[[Gerald Kuhn]] (26 saves / 27 shots)\n|date2=3 March\n|home2=2\n|score2=6\u20135\n|recap2=www.telekomeishockey.de/event/pinguins-bremerhaven-erc-ingolstadt/787\n|won2=2\n|2-1-1=12:39 \u2013 [[John Laliberte]] (PP)\n|2-1-2=[[Mike Hoeffel]] (PP) \u2013 05:24<br>[[Jack Combs (ice hockey)|Jack Combs]] (PP) \u2013 19:48\n|2-2-1=24:18 \u2013 [[David Elsner]]<br>25:59 \u2013 [[Bj\u00f6rn Svensson]] (PP)\n|2-2-2=[[Jordan Owens (ice hockey)|Jordan Owens]] \u2013 33:27<br>[[Ross Mauermann]] \u2013 33:53\n|2-3-1=40:37 \u2013 [[Brandon Buck]] (PP)<br>47:45 \u2013 [[Brian Salcido]]\n|2-3-2=Owens (PP) \u2013 41:32<br>[[Jason Bast]] (PP) \u2013 46:28\n|goalie2-1=[[Timo Pielmeier]] (28 saves / 34 shots)\n|goalie2-2=[[Gerald Kuhn]] (29 saves / 34 shots)\n|series=Bremerhaven won series 2\u20130\n}}\n\n====Eisb\u00e4ren Berlin vs. Straubing Tigers====\n{{NHLPlayoffs\n|team1=[[Eisb\u00e4ren Berlin]]\n|team2=[[Straubing Tigers]]\n|stadium1=[[Mercedes-Benz Arena (Berlin)|Mercedes-Benz Arena]], [[Berlin]]\n|stadium2=[[Eisstadion am Pulverturm]], [[Straubing]]\n|date1=1 March\n|score1=3\u20131\n|recap1=www.telekomeishockey.de/event/eisbaeren-berlin-straubing-tigers/793\n|won1=1\n|1-1-1=[[Jamie MacQueen]] (PP) \u2013 11:49\n|1-2-2=31:24 \u2013 [[Sean Sullivan (ice hockey)|Sean Sullivan]]\n|1-3-1=MacQueen \u2013 50:37<br>[[Marcel Noebels]] (ENG) \u2013 59:58\n|goalie1-1=[[Petri Vehanen]] (33 saves / 34 shots)\n|goalie1-2=[[Matt Climie]] (32 saves / 35 shots)\n|date2=3 March\n|home2=2\n|score2=2\u20133\n|ot2=3\n|recap2=www.telekomeishockey.de/event/straubing-tigers-eisb